						Climate &amp; Energy					</button>
																</div>

		<div class="g50-profile__footer">
			<div class="g50-follow g50-follow--hide-mobile">
				<a class="g50-follow__link" href="https://twitter.com/The_Emily_Show" rel="noopener" target="_blank"><i class="fab fa-twitter g50-follow__icon"></i>Follow Emily Rice</a>			</div>

